    <div id="descriptionsection" class="tabcontent">
        <a id="description" name="description"></a>
        <h3 class="section-heading">Description</h3>
        <div class="container printshow">
           
            <p>The D2757PH based on passive 3D polarization technology sets good design standards, sporting a profile of thin and a super-slim frame. Front band accents its straightforward casing, setting it apart from the monotony of most other models. But the 27" also delivers in terms of performance: able to convert 2D content into stereoscopic 3D pictures, the D2757PH with LED backlights and HDMI connectors is the ultimate media and entertainment center.</p>                        
            
            

